  12 Apr 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org>
  ruby-panel-applet-0.27.ebuild, ruby-panel-applet-0.29.ebuild,
  ruby-panel-applet-0.30.ebuild, ruby-panel-applet-0.34.ebuild:
